title: NEVER SETTLE
itunes:title: NEVER SETTLE
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
NEVER SETTLE! The minute you settle for less than you deserve, you get even less than you settled for. Powerful motivational speech featuring new speeches from speakers Marcus Taylor (https://bit.ly/MarcusTaylorMotiversity), Dr. Jessica Houston (https://bit.ly/DrJessicaHoustonMotiversity) and Walter Bond (https://bit.ly/WalterBondMotiversity).


This video was sponsored by the UAE Nation Brand Project.


Music by Really Slow Motion (https://bit.ly/RSMMusic).


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
